Class Event

java.lang.Object
Event
Direct Known Subclasses:
Concert, Festival, Sport
public abstract class Event extends Object
The `Event` class represents an abstract event with various properties and methods. This class serves as a base class for specific event types.
Since:
November 19, 2023
